This week's show is a high-energy genre-defying two hours from the dynamic duo of Graeme Sinden and Joshua Harvey, aka The Count & Sinden. They've been producing together for three years and have struck on a sound that draws on a diverse range of influences such as house, hip-hop, ragga and rave. This Essential Mix is no exception, journeying through Afrobeat, Carnival, Disco, House and Techno.
